姐今鑊仲唔爽死...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW鬼父咁樣唔單止係對學生有影響<br />\n甚至係影響埋畢左業嘅十傑喎(當然都要十傑有係日本開店)<br />\n無理由業界所有人都會順服佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔打柒佢</blockquote><br />\n一開頭唔係話左遠月係日本飲食界好大影響力咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無記錯好似操控左好多供應商<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7066a26557bab2d080fd40b3299fb9d8e9c6926","tid":313304,"uid":437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:44:47.000Z","msg":"好想女木島贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590e6fab8ec9ee44bf57400eedcfaf5cec8bc433","tid":313304,"uid":49852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"有冇可能二三席平手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8f6eafb9a55ef3c267555138db718a3756e358","tid":313304,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>創真隻食指都幾撚長下 大小姐今鑊仲唔爽死...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW鬼父咁樣唔單止係對學生有影響<br />\n甚至係影響埋畢左業嘅十傑喎(當然都要十傑有係日本開店)<br />\n無理由業界所有人都會順服佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔打柒佢</blockquote><br />\n一開頭唔係話左遠月係日本飲食界好大影響力咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無記錯好似操控左好多供應商<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係姐，但冇話皇帝一定穩如泰山嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪真係咁多人支持鬼父<br />\n連有頭有面好出名嘅高級店都要做佢隻狗？都要跟佢提供嘅餐單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e70c09da6732319bad587e3d03a3138a4a34b9","tid":313304,"uid":22645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:06:14.000Z","msg":"之前估第三席無得打二席，但今集第三席突然間變到好撚勁咁，鋪排到可以同龍膽一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji